Package: buscadoR
Type: Package
Title: Combine results from hmmer, deeptmhmm and BLAST into RLK protein predictions. 
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Dan MacLean
Maintainer: Dan MacLean <dan.maclean@tsl.ac.uk>
Description: This package will load results from hmmer, deeptmhmm, and BLAST, parse them and assign to RLK protein classes. 
    The raw input to the functions here are outputs from the above programs ideally obtained using the buscadoR Google Colab book.
    This package allows easy inspection, summaries and figures to be generated about the putative RLKs discovered.
